pattern_sources.author: Monica Fox
pattern_sources.name: Fidget Bundle
pattern_sources.notes:
The bundle includes 5 fidget patterns using 9mm pony beads:

* Fidget Bead Lanyard
* Granny Square Fidget
* Rainbow Bead Fidget
* Two-Tone Fidget Square
* Fidget Key Fob

Check each individual listing for materials and additional info. 15% off when purchasing the bundle.
